DbmI - Movie Database

DbIM is a Python based computer application, developed using PyQt and Oracle(backend), written in SQL. This is an interactive and Dynamic application that works on the Movie Database which has around half a million movies to manipulate on.

This uses PL/SQL, Triggers and efficient queries to make the working faster, both at Server and Client side.

CannaWry

CannaWry is a Ransomware developed in Python with an intention to understand the 2016 WannaCry Ransomware attack. This Ransomware encrypts the target machine entirely with a randomly created key, logged, until a simulated ransom is paid. This uses PyCrypto module to encrypt files.
